description:
Cambry and I got to try out a SELF DRIVING Power Chair that is going to change the accessibility space forever. Order the Strutt ev¹ Here: https://strutt.inc/pages/strutt-ev1?utm_source=JRE  The ev¹ is currently available at a special early-bird price of $5,299 (MSRP $7,499), a savings of $2,200 for pre-orders only.

Use code JREEV1 at checkout to get an Exclusive Accessory Bundle (~$500 Value) for FREE!

The Bundle Includes:
1x Rear Storage
2x Side Storage
1x Phone & Cup Mount
Code valid: Jan 5, 11:00 AM EST – Feb 28, 2026, Midnight EST.

We have seen Lidar sensors used in self driving cars and even robot vacuums now for years, so its super exciting to FINALLY see the high tech technology  debut in the accessibility space. Its about to benefit so many people!
